    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "\"The evaluation order of expressions is not specified (more formally, the order in which the children of one node in the expression tree are evaluated is not specified, but they are of course evaluated before the node itself). It is only guaranteed that statements are executed in order and short-circuiting for boolean expressions is done\" ( https://solidity.readthedocs.io/en/v0.5.13/control-structures.html#order-of-evaluation-of-expressions )\r\n\r\nWe might want to change that in the new code generator, though, and enforce a certain order.",
